item.title: Prayer bpn12999 in Daga
item.description: Nop ma nainit wamewa gapan waen ge apan mu dere, waenapan dere den wagup namumup yona wain, ma yogup kanamawa gwanap wan. (Kitáb-i-Aqdas) Wat Ganatam Iragi, Maman! Ipiri ma ge nao gega apanewa amba Ge nao gega waenewa iyam iyam taiyamun, Ge iyan tantan ge, Ge bagusisi gega gam amba mu baigan Ge anumunana gapan wanumop. Ayop! Wat ago mun piup ma gapan amba yaibobot Gega arewa gam mu wat aimagam mum Ge gese upuru gega gapan.
